cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

The paper proposes an efficient temporal module for action recognition in videos, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed module involves motion enhancement and temporal interaction, which are related to multimedia processing (cs.MM). The paper also focuses on reducing computational cost, which is a common concern in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the proposed module is designed to capture temporal structure effectively, which is a common problem in neural networks (cs.NE).
